snippet.title: Empire of the Ants - Release Date Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10007652

Empire of the Ants arrives on November 7th 2024 as an epic 3D Real-Time Strategy game for PlayStation 5. 

Learn more about the story and gameplay mechanics of Empire of the Ants in the new trailer. Prepare for epic battles and defend your home from the forest threats. The fate of the colony lies in your hands. 🌿🐜

#ps5 #ps5games
